profile:
Fighting fires with preventative maintenance. We clean woodburning fireplace chimneys the right way! Complete fireplace care...from sweeping to repair.
***
Family owned and operated.
Able Sweeps has provided chimney sweeping services to Calgary and surrounding areas for over 20 years and has recently changed ownership and will continue to provide the same reliable, professional service.
Fully licensed, insured & WETT certified inspector.
Our workers are competent, reliable, ethical,
and conscientious.
We guarantee quality workmanship, cleanliness
and customer satisfaction.
